div.p: Defines a Logical Element for Logical Models which has no attributes or elements. The FHIR StructureDefintion Element has an id attribute and an extension element which have in V3 another meaning.
The V3 datatype II (Instance Identifier) contains an attribute @extension.
V3 classes like ClinicalDocument, Act have an id Element.
